  "title": "R&D Assistant (Food Science/ Food Technology)",
  "description": "<p>Our esteemed client in the <strong>Manufacturing industry</strong> is seeking a <strong>R&D Assistant </strong>to join their dynamic team:</p><ul><li><strong>Employment Type: </strong>Permanent</li><li><strong>Position:</strong> R&D Assistant</li><li><strong>Location:</strong> North, Singapore</li><li><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Monday to Friday, Office Hours</li><li><strong>Salary Package:</strong> Up to $2,900 + AWS + Bonus</li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Support R&D initiatives in product formulation, development, and application.</li><li>Develop new product variations and innovative application techniques for promotional projects.</li><li>Conduct quality assessments on finished products and materials, including sensory and visual inspections.</li><li>Analyze and compare current and alternative ingredients for optimization.</li><li>Maintain lab cleanliness and ensure operational efficiency in the R&D workspace.</li><li>Assist in maintaining compliance systems (e.g., safety standards, documentation).</li><li>Prepare daily activity summaries and progress reports.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma or ITE in Culinary, Food Science, Food Technology or any other related field</li><li>At least 1 year of related working experience would be preferred. Training will be provided for inexperienced candidates.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Ready to apply? Here’s how:</strong></p><ul><li>Click the APPLY button, or</li><li>Email your resume (in MS Word or PDF format) to <strong>adelin@intuitrecruitment.com</strong>. Include the job title in your email subject line for prompt processing.</li></ul><p><em><strong>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></em></p><p><br /></p><p>By submitting your application, you consent to the collection and use of your personal data under Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p><br /></p><p>Adelin Chong | EA Personnel Reg No.: R1875641</p><p>Intuit Recruitment Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 25C2793</p>",
